FamilyDashboard Weather Icons License

This directory contains original SVG icon files created for the FamilyDashboard project.
No third-party icon files are included in this directory.

Files in this directory:
- clear.svg
- partly-cloudy.svg
- cloudy.svg
- drizzle.svg
- rain.svg
- heavy-rain.svg
- shower.svg
- snow.svg
- blizzard.svg
- thunder.svg
- fog.svg
- unknown.svg

Usage:
These icons are intended for use within this repository and its deployments.
